    <string name="nextBotGame">Next Variant Test</string>
    <string name="nextGameDescription">Hi, we are currently experimenting with rule changes for Flang. In short those are:\n\n\n- Pawn dash: pawns can hop over each other when in front of each other\n- Horse rider: pawns can go onto a horse to ride it and can also leave it again\n- Fast horse: horses don\'t get frozen when capturing a piece\n\nHere you can play against bots to experiment a bit.</string>
